%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 Wallet Owner
    participant IA as Iris Account
    participant DM as Delegation Manager
    participant CE as Caveat Enforcers
    participant RG as ReputationGate
    participant RO as Reputation Oracle
    participant Agent as 🤖 AI Agent
    participant Target as Target Contract

    Note over Agent,RO: Phase 1: Agent Registration
    Agent->>+RO: registerAgent(metadataURI)
    RO-->>-Agent: agentId (ERC-8004 NFT)

    Note over User,DM: Phase 2: Delegation Setup
    User->>DM: Sign ERC-7710 delegation<br/>(SpendingCap + Whitelist + ReputationGate)
    DM-->>User: delegation signature (offchain)

    Note over Agent,Target: Phase 3: Delegation Redemption
    Agent->>+DM: redeemDelegation(delegation, action)
    DM->>+CE: beforeHook (SpendingCap)
    CE-->>-DM: ✅ within cap
    DM->>+CE: beforeHook (ContractWhitelist)
    CE-->>-DM: ✅ target allowed
    DM->>+RG: beforeHook (ReputationGate)
    RG->>RO: getReputationScore(agentId)
    RO-->>RG: score: 87
    RG-->>-DM: ✅ above threshold
    DM->>+IA: execute(target, value, calldata)
    IA->>+Target: call(calldata)
    Target-->>-IA: result
    IA-->>-DM: success
    DM->>CE: afterHook (update spending tracker)
    DM-->>-Agent: ✅ execution complete

    Note over Agent,Target: Phase 4: Blocked Execution
    Agent->>+DM: redeemDelegation(delegation, overCapAction)
    DM->>+CE: beforeHook (SpendingCap)
    CE-->>-DM: ❌ cap exceeded
    DM-->>-Agent: revert SpendingCapExceeded

    Note over RO,RG: Phase 5: Reputation Degradation
    Note right of RO: Agent gets negative feedback
    RO->>RO: score drops to 40
    Agent->>+DM: redeemDelegation(delegation, action)
    DM->>+RG: beforeHook (ReputationGate)
    RG->>RO: getReputationScore(agentId)
    RO-->>RG: score: 40
    RG-->>-DM: ❌ below threshold
    DM-->>-Agent: revert ReputationTooLow
